1
00:00:26,100 --> 00:00:31,291
froy Lipis, ir hot frieret geredt, az men hot genumen shisn di yidn.

2
00:00:32,142 --> 00:00:36,101
dertseylt fun dem, ven men hot genumen shisn di yidn.

3
00:00:36,664 --> 00:00:38,204
oyf di vegn?

4
00:00:37,305 --> 00:00:38,615
oyfn vegn.

5
00:00:38,318 --> 00:00:44,213
hot men genemen, m'hot, nisht gelozt geyn vayter. m'hot dikh avekgenemen in der zayt ⟨un VSЁ⟩: "zits."

6
00:00:44,213 --> 00:00:49,180
un yunge zenen gegan vayter, un m'hot, un drum ze'mir opgegan etlekhe kilometer.

7
00:00:49,180 --> 00:00:51,300
ho'mir gehert, azoy me shist.

8
00:00:51,300 --> 00:00:54,450
un di mentshn vos zenen dort geblibn, eltere un kinder,

9
00:00:54,450 --> 00:00:56,233
iz keyner shoyn nisht gekumen.

10
00:00:56,593 --> 00:00:59,600
un eynike vos zenen antlofn

11
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:02,915
hobn dertseylt az me varft arayn glaykh in di griber,

12
00:01:03,040 --> 00:01:06,800
un me shist un... nor s'ershte, glavne darf men bay di,

13
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:08,580
fun dortn, di mentshn,

14
00:01:08,580 --> 00:01:11,263
vos hobn gevoynt dort, di, rusishe...

15
00:01:11,263 --> 00:01:14,772
nisht rusishe, Ukrayner, hobn dos ershte barabevet ales.

16
00:01:14,772 --> 00:01:19,110
bay zey iz geven ⟨az zey⟩ zoln zikh onnemen mit yidish guts.

17
00:01:19,110 --> 00:01:24,366
un dernokh dem hot men arayngevarfn glaykh in di griber un m'hot geshosn. vos m'hot gevolt hobn zey getun.

18
00:01:24,366 --> 00:01:27,240
dos iz shreklekh tsu dermonen!

19
00:01:27,240 --> 00:01:30,973
ikh gedenk, ven der feter undzerer iz gekumen tsu loyfn,

20
00:01:30,973 --> 00:01:32,000
borves,

21
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:38,022
un hot geveynt, nor er iz geven fun di gedanken opgemisht, un, biz er iz geshtorbn

22
00:01:38,022 --> 00:01:41,022
hot er nor geveynt un hot geshrign, azoy

23
00:01:41,022 --> 00:01:45,511
di froy zayne hot im nokhgeshrign, az zey hobn shtark sheyn opgelebt di yorn,

24
00:01:45,511 --> 00:01:49,777
azoy zi hot im nokhgeshrign, "⟨Shite⟩, vos lozstu mikh iber?"

25
00:01:50,222 --> 00:01:58,711
un er hot gornisht gekent tun. er hot nisht gevolt geyn; m'hot im geshlogn mit nahaykes er zol geyn, un naket iz er shoyn gegan. m'hot im oysgetun di ODЁZHA mit al⟨emen⟩,

26
00:01:58,711 --> 00:02:01,922
vos ⟨er iz gegan in⟩ kleyder. ot dos iz geven dentsmol

27
00:02:01,922 --> 00:02:03,395
far Molev.

28
00:02:03,570 --> 00:02:11,709
in Molev hot men undz arayngetribn. dort, gedenk ikh, ze'mir geven a bisl, un dernokh dem hot men undz genemen traybn un traybn. ze'mir gegan

29
00:02:11,709 --> 00:02:15,692
biz, biz ergets v⟨os⟩ s'hot shoyn oysgefaln der ershter shney.

30
00:02:15,692 --> 00:02:20,586
fun dorf tsu dorf. ver s'iz oyfn veg gefaln, ver krank,

31
00:02:20,586 --> 00:02:21,888
azoy iz men gegan.

32
00:02:21,888 --> 00:02:26,447
un, UNK, ir't fregn, azoy ze'mir geblibn lebn? az m'iz gegan oyf di vegn,

33
00:02:26,500 --> 00:02:31,697
f- flegn aroysgeyn di mentshn vos zey hobn gevoynt oyf der Ukrayne.

34
00:02:31,697 --> 00:02:35,756
yene zenen gebidevete mentshn; zey hobn ibergelebt a sakh.

35
00:02:35,756 --> 00:02:38,135
⟨a⟩z zey flegn zen, undz gey'mir,

36
00:02:38,135 --> 00:02:41,600
flegn zey hobn rakhmones un aroystrogn a shtikl broyt,

37
00:02:41,640 --> 00:02:45,044
oystrogn a bisl vaser. dermit ho'mir gelebt.

38
00:02:45,044 --> 00:02:48,724
eyn mol ze'mir gegangen ergets... m'- m'hot getribn,

39
00:02:48,724 --> 00:02:51,122
m'hot nisht gevust aleyn vuhin, getribn...

40
00:02:51,122 --> 00:02:52,885
ze'mir durkh aza min ⟨ot o⟩,

41
00:02:52,885 --> 00:02:54,460
geven a ritshkele.

42
00:02:54,550 --> 00:02:57,345
iz dentsmol geven i a daytshisher,

43
00:02:57,435 --> 00:03:00,005
i a Rumener hot undz getribn.

44
00:03:00,005 --> 00:03:04,638
hot er gezogt... der daytsh hot zikh epes nit shtark vegn far-, vegn, tsirung,

45
00:03:04,638 --> 00:03:06,924
nor der Rumener hot azoy gezogt:

46
00:03:06,924 --> 00:03:11,000
"ales vos hobn gold," un er iz gegan do vegn pulyes,

47
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:13,764
"zol ater araynleygn ales vos m'hot."

48
00:03:15,306 --> 00:03:20,211
m'hot moyre gehat; bald shist er dikh. az m'iz avekgegan nemen a bisl vaser UNK,

49
00:03:20,211 --> 00:03:24,176
hot men genemen un m'hot im ongevarfn aza min ⟨ot o⟩ f⟨uls⟩ mit gold.

50
00:03:24,655 --> 00:03:31,123
mayn mame iz gegan in zilberne oyringlekh vos di shvester iz avekgeforn keyn,

51
00:03:31,123 --> 00:03:33,722
Amerike, hot zi ir geshenkt far a ⟨ay⟩ndenk.

52
00:03:33,722 --> 00:03:40,300
zi hot nisht oysgetun di oyringlekh. zilber: hot zi gemeynt, neyn. un zi hot fargesn. zi iz gegan mit a shalekhl

53
00:03:40,300 --> 00:03:41,533
far der zun.

54
00:03:41,533 --> 00:03:45,087
ven ze'mir gekumen, m'- m'hot gezogt, me zol a bisl zitsn.

55
00:03:45,087 --> 00:03:48,678
⟨ze'⟩mir gezesn, hot zi gegibn a farnem azoy ⟨ot o⟩ d⟨i⟩ shalekhl.

56
00:03:48,685 --> 00:03:51,166
un ikh bin gezesn lebn ir.

57
00:03:51,958 --> 00:03:53,994
git er a makh,

58
00:03:54,439 --> 00:03:58,322
oyf rumenish hot er gegibn a makh, "un du, vos host nisht oysgetun?"

59
00:03:58,322 --> 00:04:01,667
hot zi gikh, s'iz ir geven shver oystsutun, hot zi oysgetun

60
00:04:01,667 --> 00:04:03,244
un iz gegangen,

61
00:04:03,244 --> 00:04:08,222
un hot im gezogt, "na, na!" derfar vos zi hot azoy gezogt, hot er genemen mit der nahayke

62
00:04:08,222 --> 00:04:12,366
un hot zi ongehoybn shlogn, un zi iz tsugekumen, iz zi anidergefaln.

63
00:04:12,462 --> 00:04:14,045
azoy hobn zey getun.

64
00:04:14,045 --> 00:04:17,062
zi hot poshet fargesn, zi hot gedarft di oyringlekh.

65
00:04:17,271 --> 00:04:22,828
un m'hot zikh ongenemen ful mit yidish guts. m'iz a bisl gezesn, drum vayter getribn.

66
00:04:22,828 --> 00:04:26,042
getribn, getribn, biz s'iz aroys der ershter shney.

67
00:04:26,042 --> 00:04:29,752
mir ho'mir nisht gehat keyn ODЁZHI. mir ho'mir gornisht gehat!

68
00:04:29,978 --> 00:04:32,047
u⟨n⟩ s'iz shoyn kalt geven.

69
00:04:32,053 --> 00:04:35,129
hot men undz fartribn do vu ikh hob di karte,

70
00:04:35,129 --> 00:04:37,109
in, in, ⟨ah, Makikov⟩.

71
00:04:37,521 --> 00:04:39,034
m'hot opgeteylt...

72
00:04:39,141 --> 00:04:43,233
a, geven mistome a dray hundert mentshn tsi merer.

73
00:04:43,233 --> 00:04:44,669
hot men genemen...

74
00:04:45,790 --> 00:04:49,412
oy! m'hot undz arayngetribn in dem kolkhoz,

75
00:04:51,257 --> 00:04:57,717
un m'hot tseteylt, mistome in eyn, azoy vu se fleg zayn, beheymes, hot men undz arayngetribn.

76
00:04:57,717 --> 00:05:01,522
geven mistome tsu hundert mentshn in eyn, aza ⟨min ot o lang⟩.

77
00:05:01,522 --> 00:05:03,117
m'iz gelign azoy ⟨ot o⟩,

78
00:05:03,117 --> 00:05:04,683
un der,

79
00:05:04,892 --> 00:05:09,479
 glavne⟨r⟩ funem kolkhoz hot gehat rakhmones, ⟨hot undz⟩ gegibn a bisl shtroy.

80
00:05:09,479 --> 00:05:12,328
hot men ongepakevet shtroy oyf dr'erd,

81
00:05:12,537 --> 00:05:15,554
un m'iz gelign eyner lebn andern azoy o.

82
00:05:15,554 --> 00:05:21,411
un punkt dentsmol, gedenk ikh, hot mayn, bruder's froy gedarft rodyen.

83
00:05:22,122 --> 00:05:23,266
oy!

84
00:05:23,438 --> 00:05:26,600
m'iz gelofn; dortn akegn iz geven

85
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:29,744
a bobe. zi hot nisht gevolt geyn. m'hot gezogt az s'iz epes

86
00:05:29,744 --> 00:05:32,155
umreyne mentshn, nisht keyn gute.

87
00:05:32,230 --> 00:05:37,300
vos zol men tun? zi darf rodyen; zi shrayt gevald un gevald un gevald!

88
00:05:37,300 --> 00:05:42,077
un do f⟨u⟩l MUZHCHINY. me dreyt zikh: nishto keyn betl, nishto gornit, nor oyf dr'erd.

89
00:05:42,077 --> 00:05:46,000
iker, ikh veys nit vu di brider zenen gelofn. m'hot epes gegibn,

90
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:49,504
un m'hot genemen epes a b- a betl azoyns a kleyns.

91
00:05:49,611 --> 00:05:54,754
un keyner hot nisht gevolt, m'hot nisht gehat mit vos optsudekn, az UNK, az zi zol kenen.

92
00:05:54,754 --> 00:05:59,933
iz, ⟨⟩, iz men geshtanen azoy ⟨ot o⟩ mit shmates. m'hot gehaltn, froyen, arumgenemen,

93
00:05:59,933 --> 00:06:04,103
un mayn mame un ir mame zenen geven di bobes un m'hot genemen dos kind.

94
00:06:04,103 --> 00:06:07,256
nu, vos? s'iz a meydele, s'hot geveynt,

95
00:06:07,363 --> 00:06:14,107
un s'iz geboyrn gevorn ales gut. UNK zi hot nisht gehat vos tsu gibn zeygn; zi fleg, zeygn, iz gegan blut.

96
00:06:14,198 --> 00:06:20,944
iz men gegan in dorf. zi fleg shtark veynen bay nakht, un m'iz gezesn efsher hunderter m- hundert mentshn in dem ⟨ot o⟩.

97
00:06:20,944 --> 00:06:22,258
iz men gegan,

98
00:06:22,635 --> 00:06:25,379
hot eyne gegibn a bisl melets.

99
00:06:25,420 --> 00:06:30,597
hot men gehat shoyn dos melets, hot men nisht gehat keyn shmatkele, me zol araynleygn a bisl melets,

100
00:06:30,597 --> 00:06:33,487
dos kind zol zoyfn, a bisl nisht veynen.

101
00:06:33,487 --> 00:06:37,812
iker, m'hot epes a shmatkele, nisht oystsuvashn, nisht gornisht.

102
00:06:37,812 --> 00:06:41,837
m'hot genemen dos shmatkele un m'hot arayngeshtupt dem kind in piskl,

103
00:06:41,837 --> 00:06:45,137
un dos hot ge⟨z-⟩ azoy ⟨ot o⟩ gemakht a bisl nisht veynen.

104
00:06:43,678 --> 00:06:44,752
smotshket.

105
00:06:45,137 --> 00:06:48,206
nu, vos? s'hot opgelebt tsvey vokhn, zikh nor gemutshet,

106
00:06:48,206 --> 00:06:55,062
 nisht keyn vindl, nisht in vos ⟨aynts-...⟩ un s'iz geshtorbn dos kind teykef oykhet.

107
00:06:55,508 --> 00:07:01,512
UNK do- di historye iz geven a strashne. nu, un dernokh dem ze'mir gezesn

108
00:07:01,512 --> 00:07:02,859
⟨i⟩n,

109
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:08,026
m'hot undz ge- m'hot getribn in kolkhoz, fleg men tsunoyfnemen gefroyrene kartoflyes

110
00:07:08,026 --> 00:07:13,103
mit gefroyrene burikes, un dos fleg men esn. m'iz gegan in vald, g⟨egan⟩...

111
00:07:12,855 --> 00:07:19,596
kh'vil ⟨nokh nor⟩ fregn: dos hot men aykh gegebn tsu esn, di kartoflyes, tsi ir hot aleyn ⟨,⟩ gezukht oyf...

112
00:07:16,939 --> 00:07:18,722
neyn!

113
00:07:18,846 --> 00:07:25,483
aleyn gegangen un gezukht. dos ershte hot men gezogt, mir zol'mir geyn oyf arbet. iz men gegan oyf arbet.

114
00:07:19,785 --> 00:07:22,771
⟨kha- ne- e-⟩ gef- gefunen?

115
00:07:25,483 --> 00:07:31,581
m'hot gezen az, vos ken men do oysgrobn, az s'iz shoyn ales farfroyrn gevorn? s'iz geven shtark a shverer vinter.

116
00:07:31,603 --> 00:07:36,980
az s'iz shoyn ales geven farfroyrn. vos zol men oysgrobn, az s'iz ales shoyn farfroyrn geven?

117
00:07:36,227 --> 00:07:39,292
vos hot men aykh geheysn oystsugrobn dortn?

118
00:07:38,522 --> 00:07:40,181
di burikes

119
00:07:39,754 --> 00:07:40,473
yo.

120
00:07:40,181 --> 00:07:41,957
mit di kartoflyes.

121
00:07:40,868 --> 00:07:41,857
mit di k-....

122
00:07:41,957 --> 00:07:44,505
s'iz geblibn in di felder; s'iz farfroyrn gevorn.

123
00:07:44,505 --> 00:07:48,222
un dos hot men geesn, gefroyrene kartoflyes, azoy ⟨ot o⟩, vi yoykh.

124
00:07:48,222 --> 00:07:50,745
vos zhe hot men gezolt tun? epes andersh nisht.

125
00:07:50,745 --> 00:07:51,678
nu,

126
00:07:51,803 --> 00:07:54,784
undz hot baglikt mit dermit

127
00:07:54,975 --> 00:07:57,331
vos mayn shvester hot gekent neyen.

128
00:07:57,338 --> 00:07:59,593
iz zi teykef aroys in dorf,

129
00:07:59,717 --> 00:08:01,331
un hot ongehoybn

130
00:08:01,894 --> 00:08:09,262
tsu bislekh neyen. fleg der gibn a broyt, der dos. nu, vos? m'hot es arayngebrakht un m'hot tseteylt oyf yedn. vos hot es,

131
00:08:09,537 --> 00:08:12,266
⟨⟩, gestayet? gornisht.

132
00:08:11,631 --> 00:08:16,282
dos heyst, ⟨in⟩ dem kolkhoz, dos hot men ge- a lager gerufn?

133
00:08:13,572 --> 00:08:14,595
yo?

134
00:08:17,166 --> 00:08:22,329
 dentsmol, ven m'hot undz getribn fun Molev, hot men genemen gantse kolones,

135
00:08:19,967 --> 00:08:21,125
yo.

136
00:08:22,329 --> 00:08:24,265
m'hot nisht gehat mit zey vos tsu tun,

137
00:08:24,265 --> 00:08:26,292
m'hot arayngetribn in kolkhoz.

138
00:08:26,751 --> 00:08:30,448
tsi zey hobn getrakht, m'- m'⟨iz⟩ VSЁ RAVNO oysgeshtorbn dort,

139
00:08:30,448 --> 00:08:33,010
tsi oystsushtarbn, tsi vos,

140
00:08:33,010 --> 00:08:37,218
m'hot arayngetribn in d⟨i⟩ kolkhoz. dos ershte hot men gezogt, mir ve'mir geyn arbetn mit ⟨di⟩...

141
00:08:37,218 --> 00:08:42,298
nor vos iz geven tsu arbetn? oyf di felder hobn zey aropgenemen. dos oremkeyt iz dort geven groys.

142
00:08:42,298 --> 00:08:43,721
s'iz geven Rusland.

143
00:08:43,744 --> 00:08:47,234
oremkeyt groys. gefroyrene kartoflyes.

144
00:08:47,234 --> 00:08:48,612
un derfun hot men gelebt.

145
00:08:48,612 --> 00:08:52,102
holts iz nisht geven, heytsn nisht geven mit vos.

146
00:08:52,102 --> 00:08:56,644
me fleg geyn ⟨t-⟩, ⟨iz⟩ nisht vayt a vald, ganvenen an, oyshakn a boym,

147
00:08:56,644 --> 00:08:58,710
un mit dermit hot men gedarft heytsn.

148
00:08:58,710 --> 00:09:01,121
un s'hot dokh nisht gevolt brenen ersht.

149
00:09:01,121 --> 00:09:06,000
az m'hot undz gegibn azoy a ayzerne hrubkele a kleyns... s'iz dort efsher hundert mentshn...

150
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:10,037
iz, lebn hrubkele hot men geleygt shpendlekh az s'zol zikh trikenen dos holts,

151
00:09:10,037 --> 00:09:11,943
az morgn zol zikh es tsebrenen.

152
00:09:11,943 --> 00:09:13,523
shvebelekh iz nisht geven.

153
00:09:12,748 --> 00:09:13,748
⟨⟩.

154
00:09:13,523 --> 00:09:15,570
m'hot gedarft hitn a bisele

155
00:09:15,570 --> 00:09:17,598
zhar, az me zol kenen

156
00:09:17,598 --> 00:09:20,593
morgn nokh a mol, se zol a bisl khotsh reykhern.

157
00:09:20,835 --> 00:09:25,327
un vos? lebn, az m'hot gehat a bisl mel, hot men oysgemisht

158
00:09:25,327 --> 00:09:28,409
un oyf⟨n⟩ hrubel- hrubkele hot men geklept azoy,

159
00:09:28,409 --> 00:09:33,469
fun mel oysgemisht, un dos hot men gegesn. un m'iz geven gliklekh az m'hot dos gehat.

160
00:09:33,542 --> 00:09:39,439
⟨de- dents- in, in,⟩ dortn in dem ⟨Makikov⟩, der vinter iz geven shtark ⟨a ⟩ strashn⟨e⟩.

161
00:09:39,439 --> 00:09:46,140
m'iz yeder krank gevorn mit BRYUSHNOY tif, un tif, un m'iz geshtorbn ale tog

162
00:09:46,140 --> 00:09:47,897
fil mentshn.

163
00:09:48,021 --> 00:09:54,455
un zey hobn oykh moyre gehat dortn far a epidemye, der kol- di kolkhozn, nor s'iz geven vinter,

164
00:09:54,455 --> 00:09:56,166
hobn zey nisht gevolt forn.

165
00:09:56,172 --> 00:10:00,283
 tsunoyfnemen di trupn fleg men eyn mol in tsvey, dray tog.

166
00:10:00,525 --> 00:10:04,985
un d- der grub iz geven fartik. gemakht a groyser grub,

167
00:10:04,985 --> 00:10:09,800
un dortn, flegn zey kumen oyfn shlitn. ir veyst vos heyst a shlitn?

168
00:10:08,710 --> 00:10:11,134
a shlitn. vos fort oyfn shney.

169
00:10:10,650 --> 00:10:18,415
 yo. ar⟨UNK⟩varfn di mentshn toyte, ⟨un⟩ forn zey araynvarfn atin in grub, un der grub iz vayter geven ofn.

170
00:10:18,582 --> 00:10:20,224
ver s'iz geven

171
00:10:20,224 --> 00:10:23,059
a bisl gezintere, i kinder,

172
00:10:23,059 --> 00:10:28,610
i azoyne, hobn oysgelebt, nor oysgelebt hot zeyer a kleyner protsent.

173
00:10:28,610 --> 00:10:31,727
ales iz POCHTI oysgeshtorbn. ze'mir geven

174
00:10:31,727 --> 00:10:35,688
a kolone efsher fun tsvey tsi dray hundert mentshn. efsher iz geblibn

175
00:10:35,688 --> 00:10:37,064
draysik mentshn.

176
00:10:37,279 --> 00:10:39,506
yeder iz oysgeshtorbn.

177
00:10:39,506 --> 00:10:43,402
kinder un yungs, ikh veys, ikh bin geven azoy a gezunt meydele,

178
00:10:43,402 --> 00:10:48,441
un bin geven a ⟨farkokhete⟩. ikh veys, ikh bin geblibn lebn, bin ikh geblibn lebn.

179
00:10:48,441 --> 00:10:52,730
